    "description": "<strong>您好，维修工,</strong><br><br>您被叫来修理美丽的<i>阿尔卑斯庄园酒店</i>的电梯。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/32d481df7fa5b3d9e1692283968f9565.poster.avif?t=1727447527\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/32d481df7fa5b3d9e1692283968f9565.webm?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/32d481df7fa5b3d9e1692283968f9565.mp4?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >您的任务: <strong><i>到达10层修理电梯并</i> <u>安全逃离。</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>保持警惕<br></li><li>检查每一个角落是否有异常<br></li><li>检查所有的门<br></li><li>保持勇敢</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/eef7407617cce3efc16d426e2693ec2a.poster.avif?t=1727447527\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/eef7407617cce3efc16d426e2693ec2a.webm?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/eef7407617cce3efc16d426e2693ec2a.mp4?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>重要提示:</strong> 每一个细节都很重要！异常现象可能表现为声音、物品、图像或光线的微妙变化。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/03e85942a6b11ed38efe2a44c51e1b79.poster.avif?t=1727447527\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/03e85942a6b11ed38efe2a44c51e1b79.webm?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/03e85942a6b11ed38efe2a44c51e1b79.mp4?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>发现异常了吗？立即返回紧急楼梯。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/fd96f9e6062053d7e2081cefaea67fbf.poster.avif?t=1727447527\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/fd96f9e6062053d7e2081cefaea67fbf.webm?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/fd96f9e6062053d7e2081cefaea67fbf.mp4?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏描述</h2>扮演一个被召唤来修理1930年代神秘酒店电梯的维修工。当你探索这个闹鬼的建筑的走廊时，将会遇到可怕的异常现象，并揭开其中隐藏的黑暗秘密。<br><br>您能完成任务并安全逃离吗？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >此演示版的特点</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1930年代酒店主题<br></li><li>游戏时长：10-15分钟<br></li><li>1个成就<br></li><li>10个异常现象</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >控制方式</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>WASD: 移动<br></li><li>左键: 交互<br></li><li>右键: 放大<br></li><li>Shift: 奔跑<br></li><li>ESC: 选项</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/796716508fde8058056614ddc689a275.avif?t=1727447527\" width=428 height=152 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/dee86c78a08824b0f20e663910bf50af.poster.avif?t=1727447527\" width=188 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224550/extras/dee86c78a08824b0f20e663910bf50af.webm?t=1727447527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
